text: West 11 is a 1963 British crime drama movie directed by Michael Winner and based on the 1961 novel The Furnished Room by Laura Del-Rivo. It stars Alfred Lynch, Diana Dors, Eric Portman, Freda Jackson, Finlay Currie, Brian Wilde, Kathleen Breck, Patrick Wymark, Larry Dann, David Hemmings, Francesca Annis. ==Other websites== * Category:1963 crime movies Category:1963 drama movies Category:1960s crime drama movies Category:British crime drama movies Category:Movies based on books Category:Movies directed by Michael Winner
